    public abstract class AbstractAABBDetector<E extends Collidable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BroadphaseDetector<E>
    Abstract implementation of a BroadphaseDetector providing AABB (Axis Aligned Bounding Box) detection methods.

      • setAABBExpansion

        public void setAABBExpansion(double expansion)
        Description copied from interface: BroadphaseDetector
        Sets the AABB expansion value used to improve performance of broadphase updates.

        Increasing this value will cause less updates to the broadphase but will cause more pairs to be sent to the narrowphase.

        Specified by:
        setAABBExpansion in interface BroadphaseDetector<E extends Collidable>
        Parameters:
        expansion - the expansion
